  "text": "(a) The case v 0 < 0 is discussed in [CITATION_1] , with pathwise asymptotic behaviour being considered in [CITATION_2] . It turns out in this case that all solutions converge weakly to a stationary distribution. In our market model this situation does not occur and will therefore be not considered.",
